{"tid":2438062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恐瞞人臉識別 變面App遭下架","createTime":"2021-03-08T09:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T10:03:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"060b644a30af7e86d7ba8275aa29b914e45470d6","tid":2438062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210308/P4PIIX6Q5BHWVJYT4LWSR6NMSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210308%2FP4PIIX6Q5BHWVJYT4LWSR6NMSY%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=175bca01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210308%2FP4PIIX6Q5BHWVJYT4LWSR6NMSY%2F&h=7e33412f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210308/P4PIIX6Q5BHWVJYT4LWSR6NMSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n恐瞞人臉識別 變面App遭下架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VfWXbKgT0a4g2SwZm9swqyg8_Mo=/510x351/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7GGNL4QFMRB3DGGCWHQNOURKUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVfWXbKgT0a4g2SwZm9swqyg8_Mo%3D%2F510x351%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7GGNL4QFMRB3DGGCWHQNOURKUQ.jpg&h=52d7e926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■變臉App通過AI換臉技術讓圖片「動起來」。<br />\n<br />\n「螞蟻呀嘿，螞蟻呀呼，螞蟻呀哈&sim;啊&sim;」過去一星期，這款洗腦背景音樂、加上誇張扭動的變臉AI影片，在微信、抖音等社交平台瘋狂洗版。這款名為Avatarify的變臉App，更在抖音創下29億次播放量，但本月初在蘋果中國區App store突然下架。官方未解釋原因，業界猜測可能涉及私隱安全等問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「各界名人」中毒<br />\n<br />\n據報道，用戶在App上，只需導入手機裏的人臉圖片，選擇影片模板、稍加操作，就能自動生成短片，照片中的人甚至動物會做出唱歌、擠眉弄眼等的動作，十分趣怪。連各界名人都中毒，從馬斯克、馬化騰等科技公司老闆，吳京、甄子丹等演藝明星，甚至到蒙羅麗莎等世界名畫，都唱起了「螞蟻呀嘿」的魔性音樂。<br />\n<br />\nAvatarify最早出現於去年初。當時俄羅斯程式員。。。。。 <br />\n<br />\nAvatarify上月25日正式上架內地App Store，至本月1日，佔據免費App榜單第一位。不過去到3月2日凌晨，這款App悄然從蘋果中國區App Store下架，但其餘地區仍可下載。。<br />\n。。。。。。。。只要一張照片，就可以冒充他人身份完成人臉驗證環節。<br />\n<br />\n《中國基金報》"},{"pid":"b3655cd4730fae0e84855608e21f9f0edb905a88","tid":2438062,"uid":249761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"中国式解決問題<br />\n有漏洞唔係去解決<br />\n係解決發現漏洞既人"},{"pid":"dec069608af93b2afab1d2b586c7ce20e75e6423","tid":2438062,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"廢左支那武功"},{"pid":"f2275e7780205979d39c5a6da45433658ce85514","tid":2438062,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"reface呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9498137493c85d8732b788d2f5a8188e07abbd81","tid":2438062,"uid":387026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"低級趣味..."},{"pid":"adc9e73df4fab9e2e7a09208db6a3caf5592ca5e","tid":2438062,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"中囯講私隱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e9ad7fbeb402c063c5fe7c941a116f7b4d6fea","tid":2438062,"uid":100542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"本身ig見到都唔想玩喇<br />\n咁on9<br />\n要reface只會用習近平樣"},{"pid":"90c918174e7ca64f6ee3bcc05d6daac7f3094187","tid":2438062,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSznQvn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSznQvn.gif&h=a73e637a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}